---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';

const chapters = [
  { year: 2021, title: 'Remote-first habits and cloud workplaces / 远程常态与云上工作场', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-4-2021-2025/2021-chapter-42-remote-first-habits-and-cloud-workplaces/' },
  { year: 2022, title: 'Generative AI enters public life / 生成式 AI 进入公众视野', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-4-2021-2025/2022-chapter-43-generative-ai-enters-public-life/' },
  { year: 2023, title: 'Foundation models become infrastructure / 大模型成为新基础设施', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-4-2021-2025/2023-chapter-44-foundation-models-become-infrastructure/' },
  { year: 2024, title: 'Agents begin entering workflows / Agent 开始进入工作流', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-4-2021-2025/2024-chapter-45-agents-begin-entering-workflows/' },
  { year: 2025, title: 'Human-machine collaboration becomes a basic skill / 人机协作成为新的职业基本功', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-4-2021-2025/2025-chapter-46-human-machine-collaboration-as-basic-skill/' },
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title={`${SITE_TITLE} · Volume IV`}
      description="Volume IV (2021–2025): the years when machines begin to act less like tools and more like collaborators inside work, cognition, and social coordination."
    />
    <style>
      .hero,
      .section {
        padding: 1.35rem 1.45rem;
        border-radius: 22px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--line), 0.8);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
      }
      .hero + .section,
      .section + .section {
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .lead {
        max-width: 46rem;
      }
      .chapter-list {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
      }
      .chapter-list li + li {
        margin-top: 0.45rem;
      }
      .muted {
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Volume IV / 第四卷</p>
        <h1>Machine Collaborators / 机器合作者</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          This volume follows the years when machines begin to act less like background tools and more like visible collaborators inside writing, coding, search, decision support, coordination, and ordinary cognitive work.
        </p>
        <p class="muted">
          这一卷写的是机器如何不再只是背景工具，而开始越来越像写作、编程、搜索、判断支持、协作与日常脑力劳动中的可见合作者。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Editorial note / 编辑说明</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>这一卷先收口到 2025。</strong>
          这是一个有意的边界：它让已经发生并初步沉淀的部分可以被当作历史来处理，也让 2026 年以后仍在剧烈展开的现实，继续保留在
          <em>Now Records</em> 与投稿材料里被认真记录，而不是被过早下结论。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Chapter line / 章节主线</h2>
        <ol class="chapter-list">
          {chapters.map((chapter) => (
            <li>
              {chapter.href ? (
                <a href={chapter.href}>{chapter.year}: {chapter.title}</a>
              ) : (
                <span class="muted">{chapter.year}: {chapter.title}</span>
              )}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Companion materials / 配套材料</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/blog/2026-03-23-volume-iv-launch-note/">Volume IV launch note / 第四卷启动说明</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/2026-03-23-volume-roadmap/">Volume roadmap / 项目卷路线图</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/2026-03-06-now-records-issue-1/">Now Records / 当下记录</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
